OmniScript.customHtmlTemplates:
<style>
#IPGetLicenses {
    background-color: #008080;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 13px;
}
#IPGetLicenses:hover, IPGetLicenses:active {
    background-color: #004c4c;
}

#Search .slds-page-header {
   display: none !important;
}

#Search form.slds-grid {
   padding: 25px 0 0 0;
   border-right: 0;
}

#SearchControls {
    padding: .65rem;
    background: #f3f3f3;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}

#SearchControls .vlc-control-wrapper {
    background: #fff;
}

#licenseList {
    padding-right: 0;
}

@media only screen
and (min-device-width : 768px)
and (orientation : landscape) {
#IPGetLicenses {
    height: 2.75rem;
}
#IPGetLicenses p {
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
}
}
</style>
